name: Console
details:
CONSOLE effects pedal with interchangeable cartridgesThere are 10 cartridges available for start. Each contains 3 effects.
​Cathedral - Reverb and space effects
Magic - Pitched delays
Time - Classic Mod delays
Vibrotrem - Modulation effects
Filter - Filter and Wah
Vibe - Rotary phase mods
Pitch Shifter - Octave and Pitch
Infinity - Big ambient effects
String Ringer - Audio rate modulation
Synthex-1 - Bass Synth​
Console comes with Cathedral and Magic cartridges. If that is not enough, choose any other for 20 USD each. 
https://www.eltamusic.com/console
